      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "**Structural alerts relevant to hERG:**  \n- The classic hERG pharmacophore often involves a **protonatable basic center** flanked by **two hydrophobic/aromatic regions** at an appropriate distance. This molecule lacks the basic center and lacks aromatic rings.",
