      "content": "For this molecule:\n- It would rely almost entirely on **hydrophobic contacts** plus limited H-bonding (carbonyls/alcohol).\n- Lacking a cationic center and aromatics, its **binding affinity is expected to be weak**, unless its overall lipophilicity and 3D shape happen to match the cavity exceptionally well.",
